{
  "id": "adv_main_04_02_03",
  "title": "星空編1章8話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピースとTRINITYAiLEの対戦が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day after‚ the match between",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "決まった後の、ある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace and TRINITYAiLE was decided",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.0266667885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 3.7599999667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（サニピとの対戦が決まって）\n（瑠依達はいつも以上に練習に熱が入っているな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（With the match against Sunny Peace set‚）\n（Rui and the others are more motivated than usual to practice）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（三人とも凄い気迫で、ライブバトルに懸ける）\n（意気込みがひしひしと伝わってくる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（All three of them are incredibly passionate‚ and they can really feel）\n（their enthusiasm for the live battle）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2666.666666600001,
          "startTime": 16.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、おはようございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1333329758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、mihoさん？　どうしたんですか？\n今日はスリクスの練習はなかったはずですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ miho-san? What's up?\nThere wasn't supposed to be any practice for ⅢX today",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は{user}さんに\nお願いしたいことがあって来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ I have something\nto ask of you‚ {user}-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "今度のサニピのライブバトルですが\n私も観たいので関係者席を確保してもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Regarding the upcoming Sunny Peace live battle\nI'd like to see it too‚ so could you secure me a seat for the official?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは構いませんが、mihoさんが他のグループの\nライブバトルを観たがるなんてめずらしいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's fine‚ but it's rare for miho-san to want to\nwatch other group's live battles",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "じきに始まるVENUSグランプリで\nサニーピースは必ず勝ち上がってきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The VENUS Grand Prix starts soon\nSunny Peace will definitely advance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "当然私達も勝ち上がるので、いずれ戦うことになる\n将来の対戦相手を偵察するのは当然の戦略です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ we'll advance as well‚ so we'll eventually face each other\nScouting future opponents is a natural strategy",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "映像だけでなく、自分の目で直接確認したいなんて\nそれだけサニピを高く評価しているんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You want to see them for yourself‚ not just watch video\nThat's how highly you rate Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "たとえまぐれでも一度は私達に勝っていますから\n警戒するのは当たり前のことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it was a luck一 they beat us once\nIt's natural to be wary",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "ⅢXのポリシーは絶対勝利\n同じ相手に二度負ける訳にはいきません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX's policy is always win\nWe can't afford to lose to the same opponent twice",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 76.0666663092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "さっきからサニピサニピて\nうちらのことは眼中にないみたいな言い方ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been saying Sunny Peace‚ Sunny Peace‚\nyou say we don't even care",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 200.00035750000222,
          "startTime": 76.2666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1333.3336908000035,
          "startTime": 77.4
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4200.000357500002,
          "startTime": 80.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "……聞いていたの？\n気を悪くしたのなら申し訳ないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Were you listening?\nI'm sorry if that sounded bad‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "貴方達に警戒するほどの価値はないわ\n私は弱者に構ってるほど暇じゃないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You guys aren't worth being wary of\nI'm not free enough to get involved with the weak",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルが弱いって言うんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you saying TRINITYAiLE is weak?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0999996425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "うちらはBIG4に次ぐランキング五位です\nそれでも実力不足なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're ranked fifth‚ just after the BIG4\nStill‚ are our skills lacking?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "格下ばかり相手にして上げたランキングに\nどれほどの価値があると言うのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder how much value there is in a ranking\nthat was achieved by competing against inferior opponents",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "ランキング五位との対戦だって、紙一重の辛勝だった\nトリエルが勝てたのは、単に運が良かっただけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even your match against the 5th ranked opponent just won by a nose\nTRINITYAiLE's win was simply a matter of luck",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9666663092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（俺は僅差でも気にしなかったが、瑠依は上にいくには）\n（もっと大差で圧倒出来なければと感じていたのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I didn't mind a narrow victory‚ but Rui felt that）\n（she needed to overwhelm her opponents by a much landslide victory to go up?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 127.3666708868
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロの他のグループは皆、BIG4になったわ\nサニピも、月ストも、貴方達に負けたリズノワでさえ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All the other groups in Hoshimi Prods. became the BIG4\nSunny Peace‚ Moon Tempest‚ and even LizNoir who lost to you guys",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.706021993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達はアイドルとしての核となるものを手に入れた\nだから強くなれた、BIG4になれた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They all found their core as idols\nThat's why they were able to become strong and become part of the BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "それに比べてトリエルには核になるものが見当たらない\nそんな相手に怖さは感じないし、負ける気はしないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In comparison‚ TRINITYAiLE has no core\nI don't feel scared of such an opponent‚ and I don't feel like I can lose",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "っ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.4333375534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない！　瑠依ちゃんも優ちゃんも\n凄く成長してる！　二人とも凄く強くなってる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true! Rui-chan and Yu-chan\nhave grown so much! Both become so much stronger!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_02_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "誰よりも高く飛ぶために頑張ってる二人を\n否定する人は私が許さないんだから！！",
      "translations": {
